 DemoGridKeyPress connected;values;F;colTitles;rowTitles;cellWidths;cellTypes
 EWC.CONNECTED‚Üêconnected
 ‚éïPW‚Üê1000

‚çù Duplicate-KeyPress repro for Grid (review finding #14).
‚çù KeyPress is registered on BOTH the grid (F1.G) AND the embedded text Edit
‚çù template (F1.G.E1). The callback CBGridKey logs a DISTINCT line per source
‚çù (GRID vs EDIT), so a human/test can count how many KeyPress events fire for a
‚çù single keystroke typed inside an Edit cell.
‚çù   - With the client fix (Grid suppresses its grid-level KeyPress while the
‚çù     keystroke originates in an embedded editor): ONE 'EDIT' line per char.
‚çù   - Without the fix: a 'GRID' line AND an 'EDIT' line ‚Äî the duplicate.
‚çù Idioms: DemoGrid.aplf:8-9,31,35,51,56,62 (Form/grid/Input/CellTypes/grid
‚çù event) and Demo_Issue250.aplf:11 (KeyPress on the embedded Edit child).

 F‚Üê'F1'
 F eWC'Form' 'Grid KeyPress Duplicate Repro'(50 50)(450 540)('Coord' 'Pixel')

‚çù Sample data: 4 rows x 2 columns ‚Äî Col1 text Edit, Col2 numeric Edit
 values‚Üê4 2‚ç¥‚ç¨
 values[1;]‚Üê'Apple' 150
 values[2;]‚Üê'Banana' 250
 values[3;]‚Üê'Cherry' 50
 values[4;]‚Üê'Date' 75

 colTitles‚Üê'Product' 'Quantity'
 rowTitles‚Üê‚ç≥4
 cellWidths‚Üê120 90

‚çù Create the Grid and register KeyPress (+ CellMove for context) on the GRID.
 (F,'.G')eWC'Grid'('Posn'(70 20))('Size'(150 280))('Values' values)('ColTitles' colTitles)('RowTitles' rowTitles)('CellWidths' cellWidths)('TitleWidth' 40)('CurCell'(1 1))('VScroll' ¬Ø1)

‚çù Embedded Input templates (children of the grid). The text Edit ALSO registers
‚çù KeyPress ‚Äî it is the second potential source per keystroke.
 (F,'.G.E1')eWC'Edit' ''('Event' 'KeyPress' 'CBGridKey')
 (F,'.G.E2')eWC'Edit'('FieldType' 'Numeric')

‚çù Wire the Input array + CellTypes matrix (1-based indices into Input).
 (F,'.G')eWS'Input'((F,'.G.E1')(F,'.G.E2'))
 cellTypes‚Üê4 2‚ç¥1 2
 (F,'.G')eWS'CellTypes' cellTypes

‚çù Register events on the grid (each event name once ‚Äî EWC/eventOK.aplf rejects
‚çù duplicate names on a single object; the duplicate we want is ACROSS objects).
 (F,'.G')eWS'Event'(‚äÇ'KeyPress' 'CBGridKey')
 (F,'.G')eWS'Event'(‚äÇ'CellMove' 'CBGridKey')

‚çù Info labels
 (F,'.Info1')eWC'Label' 'KeyPress registered on BOTH grid (F1.G) and Edit (F1.G.E1).'(20 20)(18 490)
 (F,'.Info2')eWC'Label' 'Click the Product cell, type a character: each line below = one KeyPress fired.'(40 20)(18 490)

‚çù Event log label (read+rewrite Caption to prepend, per CBGrid.aplf:54-55)
 (F,'.LogTitle')eWC'Label' 'KeyPress Log:'(230 20)(18 120)
 (F,'.Log')eWC'Label' '(events appear here)'(252 20)(180 490)
